1. 下载beyond compare for linux debian
   http://www.scootersoftware.com/download.php

   sudo dpkg -i bcompare-4.3.3.24545_amd64.deb

2. 破解
   https://www.cnblogs.com/bluestorm/p/10259441.html

3. 设置git difftool mergetool

	vim ~/.gitconfig

	[diff]
		tool = bc
	[difftool]
		prompt = false
	[merge]
		tool = bc
	[mergetool]
		prompt=false

4.使用
  git difftool
